babel - transpillar

init npm - npm init -y

init babel - npm install babel-cli babel-core babel-preset-es2015 --save-dev
cli - command line interface - use babel in command line
core - main module of babel
preset-es2015 - module for es6
--save-dev - insert to package.json

CLI
in package.json change 'test' to "build": "babel src -d dist --preset es2015"
invoke transpiller in command line - npm run build
for watching use -w at the end

GULP
npm install --save-dev gulp-babel babel-preset-es2015